snippet.title: Nice Mario 75 | Release Trailer + Download
snippet.description:
Download with ROMHACKING.com:
https://romhacking.com/hack/nice-mario-75

If you need a patcher in any sorta way use this patcher by Kaze to patch your own SM64 Rom:
https://hack64.net/tools/patcher.php

--------------------------------------------------
Music by DJMykah:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BbYE9RDPOIE
--------------------------------------------------
Info:
It took me more than 3 years of work, to get this hack to where it is today.
Sadly I abandoned this project about 3-4 years ago. Originally I wanted to make a complete hack with 120 stars but I just finished 101, though there still are the vanilla vanish cap and vanilla metal cap stages, which means I only made 99 completly new stars. There are still a lot of things I wished I could've changed before uploading this hack, but I am not able to use the tools to change those things anymore. They're just too old...
I still hope you like this traditional hack and have fun with it!
--------------------------------------------------
#SM64 #Hacks #Release
